/news/music/got7-reunite-nanana-music-video-self-titled-mini-album-ep-release-3231378">主打单曲《Nanana》</a>回归。</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/got7-bambam-2023-2024-area-52-world-tour-tickets-venues-cities-3467708">GOT7的BamBam在2023年至2024年“Area 52”世界巡演中增加了新城市，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
