sts/jinsoul">Jinsoul</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/choerry">Choerry</a>主演的 LOONA 子队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/odd-eye-circle">Odd Eye Circle</a>最近在由前 LOONA 创意总监 Jaden Jeong 创立的韩国流行音乐机构<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/modhaus">Modhaus</a>旗下<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/odd-eye-circle-version-up-loona-artms-3456298">推出了《Version Up》，首次回归</a>。</p><p>与此同时，据报道，首尔一家法院在前 LOONA 成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chuu">Chuu</a>针对 Blockberry Creative 的合同诉讼中做出了有利于她的裁决。距离韩国流行音乐机构<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chuu-fired-from-loona-alleged-violent-language-misuse-power-agency-blockberry-creative-3355729">将这位歌手从女子组合中除名</a>已近一年。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/loossemble-official-debut-september-2023-loona-3485835">Loossemble 将于今年 9 月正式亮相，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
